# 8. Test Nginx

Local

```bash
curl http://127.0.0.1
```

Host header

```bash
curl -H "Host: crm.example.com" http://127.0.0.1
```

HTTPS

```bash
curl -Ik https://127.0.0.1 -H "Host: crm.example.com"
```

