# Common Problems

## 403 Forbidden

Usually

* Wrong permissions
* Wrong root folder

Root must be

```
project/public
```

NOT

```
project/
```

---

## 404 Not Found

Usually

* Incorrect root
* Missing try_files directive

---

## Permission denied

Fix

```bash
sudo chown -R ubuntu:www-data storage bootstrap/cache

sudo chmod -R 775 storage bootstrap/cache
```

---

## File not found

Usually

Wrong

```
root /project
```

Correct

```
root /project/public
```

---

## PHP downloaded instead of executed

PHP-FPM not configured correctly.

Verify

```bash
sudo systemctl status php8.5-fpm
```

---

## php8.5-fpm.sock missing

Restart PHP

```bash
sudo systemctl restart php8.5-fpm
```

---

## 502 Bad Gateway

Usually

* PHP-FPM stopped
* Wrong socket path
* Wrong PHP version

Verify

```bash
ls /run/php/
```

---

## ERR_SSL_PROTOCOL_ERROR

Usually

* HTTP served on HTTPS port
* SSL certificate missing
* Wrong certificate path

---

## Cloudflare 522

Usually

* AWS Security Group blocks port 80/443
* UFW blocks HTTP/HTTPS
* Nginx not listening
* DNS incorrect

---

## Could not resolve host

DNS record missing.

Create

```
A crm -> Public IP
```

---

## Certbot Unauthorized

Usually

* DNS incorrect
* Cloudflare proxy issue
* HTTP challenge cannot reach the server

Verify

```bash
curl http://crm.example.com
```

before requesting a certificate.

