# Useful Commands

Restart Nginx

```bash
sudo systemctl restart nginx
```

Reload Nginx

```bash
sudo systemctl reload nginx
```

Restart PHP

```bash
sudo systemctl restart php8.5-fpm
```

Restart Queue Worker

```bash
sudo systemctl restart crm-worker
```

View PHP logs

```bash
sudo journalctl -u php8.5-fpm -f
```

View Queue logs

```bash
sudo journalctl -u crm-worker -f
```

Test configuration

```bash
sudo nginx -t
```

List PHP sockets

```bash
ls -l /run/php/
```

View loaded Nginx configuration

```bash
sudo nginx -T
```

